This paper discusses the management of files and resources in a distributed computing environment, which is a common topic in the field of Distributed Computing (cs.DC). The use of a distributed file catalogue and job resource broker also involves aspects of Data Management (cs.DL) and Database Systems (cs.DB). The use of a File Transport Broker and Job Resource Broker also involves aspects of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the implementation of the brokers and their architecture involves aspects of Software Engineering (cs.SE).
